description:
This is part 2 of the very special Everything Iconic POP Dive into the life and work of Tyra Banks. In part 2, Danny & guest Annabelle DeSisto explore Tyra's role in Life Size and the upcoming sequel, the best of her iconic self-titled talk show, and SO much more.


*To support this podcast and for bonus episodes, visit Patreon.com/EverythingIconic
